Our Team - Woodley Farra Manion Portfolio Management











































  
Skip to content


























						Close Menu
					









Your Financial Coaches
Located on the north side of Indianapolis and founded in 1995, Woodley Farra has more than 100 years of combined investment management experience. We are a Registered Investment Advisor (RIA) with the SEC. We conduct all our own research in-house, focusing on individual securities. In addition, several members of our team have earned the title Chartered Financial Analyst* (“CFA”), providing our clients with an extra measure of confidence.
When visitors walk into our offices, they are often surprised at the open structure. Financial advisors sit at their desks in a common area along with the rest of the staff. As we’ve grown, we’ve taken our style from our roots: Don and George sharing one office, working side by side. We find we do better work for our clients when we aren’t sequestered in offices but rather functioning together as a team.
And while we embrace transparency and a collegial, team approach, we value our clients’ personal information and treat it with the utmost confidentiality.
Get to know us, and then give us a call. We’d love to get to know you.
*When clicking this link, you are leaving Woodley Farra Manion’s website and entering a third-party website. This third-party website is not affiliated with, sponsored by, or endorsed by Woodley Farra Manion. We make no representation as to the completeness or accuracy of information provided in these websites, nor are we liable for any direct or indirect technical or system issues arising out of your access or use of third-party technologies, websites, information and programs made available through this website.











