Company Overview of Woodley Farra Manion Portfolio Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Woodley Farra Manion Portfolio Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to Individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, trusts, estates, charitable organizations, and corporations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. The firm primarily invests in dividend paying value stocks of large-cap companies with market capitalizations over $1 billion. For its fixed income portfolios, it uses investment grade bonds, FDIC-insured, bank CDs and preferred securities of financially so...
Woodley Farra Manion Portfolio Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to Individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, trusts, estates, charitable organizations, and corporations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. The firm primarily invests in dividend paying value stocks of large-cap companies with market capitalizations over $1 billion. For its fixed income portfolios, it uses investment grade bonds, FDIC-insured, bank CDs and preferred securities of financially solid companies. The firm employs fundamental, technical, quantitative, and economics analysis to make its investments. It conducts in-house research to make its investments. Woodley Farra Manion Portfolio Management, Inc. was founded in 1995 and is based in Indianapolis, Indiana.
Detailed Description


